Parental Bond

Parent and child each attacks.

Affected Moves

All single-strike damaging moves qualify for the child strike, except the following.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Drag To The Void 10 80 100 The user takes the target into darkness, then damages it during the next turn.
Dragon Darts 10 50 100 The user attacks twice using Dreepy. In case of two targets, each is hit once.
Dynamax Cannon 5 100 100 The user unleashes a strong beam that deals deals double damage to Dynamaxed targets.
Endeavor 5 — 100 This attack move cuts down the target's HP to equal the user's HP.
Explosion 5 250 100 The user attacks everything around it by causing a massive explosion but also faints.
Final Gambit 5 — 100 The user risks everything, fainting but inflicting damage equal to its HP.
Fling 10 — 100 The user flings its held item at the target. This move's power and effects depend on the item.
Ice Ball 20 30 90 The user attacks the target for five turns. The move's power increases each time it hits.
Rollout 20 30 90 The user continually rolls into the target over five turns. It becomes stronger each hit.
Self-Destruct 5 200 100 The user attacks everything around it by causing an explosion but also faints.
